<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.10">
<l>tēmaruvu poḻilpuṭaicūḻ tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>vāmaṉaṉai maṟikaṭalcūḻ vayalāli vaḷanāṭaṉ</l>
<l>kāmarucīrk kalikaṉṟi kaṇṭuraitta tamiḻmālai</l>
<l>nāmaruvi yivaipāṭa viṉaiyāya naṇṇāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [one] sings these Tamil verses, familiarizing [them] to the tongue,</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem, the one of fertile Āli country</l>
<l rend="indent">with fields encircled by the rolling sea,</l>
<l>Having seen Vāmana who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram girded on [all] sides</l>
<l>By groves embraced by fragrance, existent karma will not adhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
